Ibikoro ni bimwe mu biribwa bitaboneka cyane ariko bifitiye umubiri wacu akamaro kanini. Ni kimwe mu bihangwa bikurira mu butaka nk’imyumbati n’ibijumba.

Hari abantu bitiranya ibikoro n’ibijumba ariko burya biratandukanye. Ibikoro bikungahaye ku ntugamubiri zitandukanye nka vitamini, imyunyungugu, ibinyasukari na poroteyine. Ni byiza kandi ku muntu wabujijwe amavuta na muganga kuko nta binure bigira. Ikindi ni uko ari ibiribwa byoroshye gutekwa.

